VendorMerge is a BusinessTask
    owned by ap

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                VendorMergeReport

    Parameters
        VendorGroup             
        FromVendor              is a Vendor
        ToVendor                is a Vendor
        Update                  is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        RptOption               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Detail  value is "D"
                Summary value is "S"
        PoinvoiceOption         is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        IncludeArchive          is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                ExcludeArchive value is "N"
                IncludeArchive value is "Y"
        CreateComments          is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        Upd1099                 is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        MrgAllHistory           is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        FromDate                is Date
        ToDate                  is Date

    Parameter Rules
        VendorGroup
            required
        FromVendor
            required
        ToVendor
            required
        Update
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        RptOption
        	initial value is "D"
            default to "D"
        PoinvoiceOption
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        IncludeArchive
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        CreateComments
        	initial value is "Y"
            default to "Y"
        Upd1099
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        MrgAllHistory
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"

    Actions
        VendorMerge is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
